{"tid":1952979,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Zoom 被指誤導用家　視像會議非點到點加密 英國防部曾表明不支持使用","createTime":"2020-04-01T02:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T03:59:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"03500f6449d6f01dfaab6f8ace4271ceccf187c4","tid":1952979,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:12:15.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯Zoom 同樣在其網站及保安白皮書上聲稱軟件支援點到點加密，以確保用戶私隱得以保障。不過，The intercept 向 Zoom 查詢時，該公司發言人則表示，現時未能為視像會議提供點對點加密。實際上 Zoom 在視像會議採用的是一種名為傳輸層安全性協定 (Transport Layer Security, TLS) 的加密方法。此加密方法只確保用戶數據傳輸至 Zoom 期間被加密。<br />\n<br />\n不過  Zoom 就否認該公司有誤導用家，並指他們所指的「點對點」是指 Zoom 程式兩端傳輸已被加密 (it is in reference to the connection being encrypted from Zoom end point to Zoom end point) 。約翰&middot;霍普金斯大學密碼學家及電腦科學家 Matthew Green 就指出，視像會議本身較難以作點對點加密，關鍵是軟件需要判斷到哪個用家在說話。他舉例，蘋果的 FaceTime 就做到點對點加密通訊。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\nGreen 認為 Zoom 對於他們所指的點對點加密說法有點模糊，並認為此舉有點「不誠實</span></strong>」⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\nZoom 是由前 Cisco 工程部門副總裁<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">袁征</span></strong>創立，在此之前他曾負責 Cisco 通訊軟件 WebEx 開發。<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\nConsumer Reports, Zoom Calls Aren't as Private as You May Think. Here's What You Should Know, 30 March 2020<br />\nThe Intercept, Zoom Meetings Aren&rsquo;t End-To-End Encrypted, Despite Misleading Marketing, 31 March 2020<br />\n<br />\n文／Edward Ho、審核／Anita Chow<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/technology/zoom-%E7%96%91%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%8E%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E8%A6%96%E5%83%8F%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E9%9D%9E%E9%BB%9E%E5%88%B0%E9%BB%9E%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2Fzoom-%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25B0%258E%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2583%258F%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E9%259D%259E%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25AF%2586%2F&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhiSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=32c47366\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2Fzoom-%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25B0%258E%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2583%258F%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E9%259D%259E%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25AF%2586%2F&h=38916550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/technology/zoom-%E7%96%91%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%8E%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E8%A6%96%E5%83%8F%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E9%9D%9E%E9%BB%9E%E5%88%B0%E9%BB%9E%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86/</a>"},{"pid":"fc271736b03e2efa24b4cc022d55e796093a1207","tid":1952979,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:13:26.000Z","msg":"中國產品係咁"},{"pid":"3731f9ebf87d58acaae502cdaa125c6ac1fc33b9","tid":1952979,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:21:49.000Z","msg":"中國國家安全法第14條<br />\n<br />\n情報機關有權要求個人，企業<br />\n對情報機關提出要求提供協助，支援<br />\n<br />\n所有中國人都應該視為潛在中共間諜<br />\n即係話zoom的視頻可能變哂中共的資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要採取麥卡錫主義嚴打"},{"pid":"c95ba1f87eeaed0ace312fcf03d3efd04ebcefbf","tid":1952979,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:24:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d3163d47b804c99c0d101eb290bbc3e048f8ee77","tid":1952979,"uid":58852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3731f9ebf87d58acaae502cdaa125c6ac1fc33b9","tid":1952979,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:21:49.000Z","msg":"中國國家安全法第14條<br />\n<br />\n情報機關有權要求個人，企業<br />\n對情報機關提出要求提供協助，支援<br />\n<br />\n所有中國人都應該視為潛在中共間諜<br />\n即係話zoom的視頻可能變哂中共的資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要採取麥卡錫主義嚴打"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:43:58.000Z","msg":"嚴格來講zoom係美帝公司<br />\n但係芝麻人唔排除係間諜"},{"pid":"f2322e41e76cca6ba46cdb974dd5ab09ea596d1b","tid":1952979,"uid":42108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3163d47b8